# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:12
translate portuguese english0_91385abf:

    # "I find an empty seat and take a look around the room."
    "Encontro um lugar vazio e dou uma olhadela pela sala."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:15
translate portuguese english0_97c771fd:

    # "There's a girl sitting on the other side of the room that looks familiar, but I can't place her."
    "Há uma rapariga sentada do outro lado da sala que me parece familiar, mas não consigo identificá-la."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:17
translate portuguese english0_86b996c1:

    # "When it's time to start, my teacher steps in front of the class and writes her name on the dry-erase board."
    "Quando chega a hora de começar, a minha professora coloca-se à frente da turma e escreve o nome dela no quadro branco."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:19
translate portuguese english0_8e1e74f7:

    # et "Hello everyone. My name is Mrs. McGee and I'll be teaching you about comprehension and composition this year."
    et "Olá a todos. Chamo-me Sra. McGee e vou ensinar-vos compreensão e composição este ano."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:20
translate portuguese english0_6361f1f7:

    # "She seems to be in her mid-40s and looks a little exotic with her long hair, dark eyes, and that strange medallion hanging over her breasts."
    "Ela parece ter cerca de 45 anos e tem um ar um pouco exótico, com o cabelo comprido, os olhos escuros e aquele medalhão estranho pendurado sobre o peito."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:21
translate portuguese english0_0f966d91:

    # "She goes on to discuss the things we will be learning throughout the semester."
    "Ela continua a falar sobre o que vamos aprender ao longo do semestre."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:24
translate portuguese english0_400ee607:

    # "The pretty girl sitting next to me is intently focused on everything that Mrs. McGee says, writing non-stop into a notebook."
    "A rapariga bonita sentada ao meu lado está totalmente concentrada em tudo o que a Sra. McGee diz, escrevendo sem parar num caderno."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:27
translate portuguese english0_73f47a82:

    # "Should I be taking notes? Maybe... but I'm not."
    "Devo tomar notas? Talvez... mas não estou a fazê-lo."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:29
translate portuguese english0_8c862eca:

    # "When the class is over, I pack up my stuff and move on to the next class."
    "Quando a aula termina, arrumo as minhas coisas e sigo para a aula seguinte."

# game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:30
translate portuguese english0_998f20ff:

    # "The rest of my classes for the day are boring and uneventful. I breeze my way through them and then leave for the day."
    "O resto das minhas aulas do dia são aborrecidas e sem incidentes. Passo por elas sem grande esforço e depois saio."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:2
    old "This scene will happen automatically on your first day of school."
    new "Esta cena vai acontecer automaticamente no teu primeiro dia de aulas."

    # game/Scenes/School/English/english0.rpy:3
    old "Just go to school on Monday morning."
    new "Basta ires para a escola na segunda-feira de manhã."

